Package: zonator
Type: Package
Title: Utilities for Zonation spatial conservation prioritization software
Version: 0.3.10
Date: 2013-02-03
Author: Joona Lehtomaki
License: BSD-2
Encodcing: UTF-8
Maintainer: Joona Lehtomaki <joona.lehtomaki@gmail.com>
Description: zonator is a utility R package for dealing with various tasks
    related to Zonation conservation prioritization software. The package
    started out as a collection of helper scripts which have now been packages
    for anybody interested in using a familiar tool (R) in setting up Zonation
    runs and managing Zonation results.
Depends:
    R (>= 2.15.2),
    methods
Suggests:
    testthat,
    knitr
Imports:
    ggplot2,
    plyr,
    RColorBrewer,
    raster,
    rgdal,
    reshape2,
    tools
BugReports: https://github.com/jlehtoma/zonator/issues
VignetteBuilder: knitr
